				<quoted-block display-inline="no-display-inline" id="idE6CCD3E4B9564BCB986F844E6706CC71" style="OLC">
 <paragraph commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="idD40CF6E08186488A882D82DEF829DAF5"><enum>(3)</enum><header display-inline="yes-display-inline">Exclusions not applicable</header><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">For purposes of the application of standards and other requirements described in paragraph (1) to a Federal research facility or any other department, agency, or instrumentality of the United States having laboratory animal facilities, the exclusions contained in section 2(g)(3) shall not apply.</text></paragraph><after-quoted-block>.</after-quoted-block></quoted-block></paragraph></section></legis-body></bill>


